        "title": "Restful Webservice does not answer",
        "body": "<p>I am new to web service programming and running in trouble. After searching the web for two days i am totally confused and my example does not provide any data to me. <\/p>\n\n<p>I want to write a restful web service that should run on tomcat 7 or glassfish 4. <\/p>\n\n<p>Here my code:<\/p>\n\n<p><strong>SimpleService.class<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>@Path(\"say\")\npublic class SimpleService {\n\n    @Path(\"hello\")\n    @GET\n    public String doGreet() {\n        return \"Hello Stranger, the time is \"+ new Date();\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><strong>web.xml<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;\n&lt;web-app xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xmlns=\"http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/javaee\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/javaee http://xmlns.jcp.org/xml/ns/javaee/web-app_3_1.xsd\" version=\"3.1\"&gt;\n  &lt;display-name&gt;test002&lt;/display-name&gt;\n  &lt;servlet&gt;\n    &lt;servlet-name&gt;Jersey Web Application&lt;/servlet-name&gt;\n    &lt;servlet-class&gt;org.glassfish.jersey.servlet.ServletContainer&lt;/servlet-class&gt;\n    &lt;load-on-startup&gt;1&lt;/load-on-startup&gt;\n  &lt;/servlet&gt;\n  &lt;servlet-mapping&gt;\n    &lt;servlet-name&gt;Jersey Web Application&lt;/servlet-name&gt;\n    &lt;url-pattern&gt;/you/*&lt;/url-pattern&gt;\n  &lt;/servlet-mapping&gt;\n&lt;/web-app&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>The request on http.//localhost:8070/test002/you/say/hello gets an 404. <\/p>\n",
